  <summary>7/27/1995--Introduced.
Amends the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to provide that community college employees in classified positions are not required to receive overtime compensation for additional service, on their own volition, in a certified or other academic capacity, unless they are employed in such positions for more than 40 hours in a week.</summary>
